3.2a Configure simple OSPFv2/v3 environments, including multiple normal areas,
summarization, and filtering (neighbor adjacency, point-to-point, and broadcast
network types, and passive-interface)


OSPF ( open shortest path first) Notes

Broadcast | Non Broadcast use DR\BDR

LSA Types: 
1 Router LSA
2 Network LSA
3 Summary LSA
4 ASBR summary LSA
5 Autonomous system LSA

OSPF Cost is calculated with the reference bandwidth over interface bandwidth
usually is 100 Mbps as default.
You can change the cost of an interface as well. 



